  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to investigate the effect of personalised exercise interventions in&#xD;
      liver transplant candidates, aiming to prevent or limit sarcopenia and frailty, as well as&#xD;
      improving their cardiorespiratory health.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
